_sText: Remake of fy_flashlighttag.  More on the way.  Map is dark so its a must that you use your flashlight in order to navigate the map (thats what gives it its name).  Night vistion helps a little too so you can pick up other peoples flashlights better.  The only reason there are lights on the map are, so you can tell what spawn you are at so you dont keep going around and around.
